Step Functions is a product that can act as the glue between microservices in AWS. 
It allows for the orchestration of Lambda functions, human interaction, and other AWS resources in a visual workflow way. 
It offers features similar to Simple Workflow Service (SWF) but does so without any long-running compute instances such as EC2

Step functions is a serverless visual workflow service that provides state machine